<template>
  <v-card>
    <v-layout>
      <router-view />
    </v-layout>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'

export default {
  name: 'App',
  created() {
    axios.get('/translation_nav')
      .then(response => {
        const navData = response.data
        console.log(navData)
      })
      .catch(error => {
        console.error(error);
      })

      axios.get('/translation_master')
      .then(response => {
        const navData = response.data
        console.log(navData)
      })
      .catch(error => {
        console.error(error);
      })

      axios.get('/translation_site_name')
      .then(response => {
        const navData = response.data
        console.log(navData)
      })
      .catch(error => {
        console.error(error);
      })
  }
}
</script>

<style>
* {
  user-select: none;
}
</style>
